title: You Don't Know Jack (UK)
description:
You Don&#039;t Know Jack (UK) 
========================

"The irreverent quiz show party game!"



-----------------------
Hey you? Yeah we mean you, Mr big I-Own-A-CD-ROM head. Think you&#039;re pretty smart don&#039;t you? Think you know your trivia, don&#039;t you? Well think again.

YOU DON&#039;T KNOW JACK is the award winning, irreverent, fast-paced game show that has taken the US by storm, and now the UK has the chance to get its fingers on the buzzers. It&#039;s got excitement, suprises, manic humour, feverish activity and more hidden features than a masked ball. Get ready - we&#039;re going to suck trivia from your brain with a big straw.

YOU DON&#039;T KNOW JACK can be played by one to three players. The goal of YOU DON&#039;T KNOW JACK is to rack up the cash. Get the most cash and you win. It&#039;s that simple, except, it isn&#039;t.
-----------------------



Released 1997

Mount the .mds file with Daemon Tools (http://www.daemon-tools.cc) to play.
